Ext.data.JsonP['Rolling_Back_a_File_Version']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Rolling Back a File Version</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n\t\t<div id=\"banner\" class=\"confbox admonition admonition-note aui-message warning shadowed information-macro\">\n\t\t\t<p>You can now find Appcelerator documentation at <a href=\"https://docs.axway.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.axway.com/</a>. This site will be taken down in the near future.</p></div>\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-30083314\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Rolling Back a File Version</h1>\n    <p>You can roll back the version of a file in your projects to an earlier version by replacing the current file version with another version from the local file history.    </p>\n    <p>To roll back the version of a file:    </p>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>In the <strong class=\" \">Project Explorer</strong> View, right-click on the file whose history you want to display, or right-click the file currently open in the editor.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>From the pop-up context menu, select <strong class=\" \">Replace With &gt; Local History...</strong> to open a <strong class=\" \">Compare</strong> pop-up window. (To roll the file back only one version, you can select <strong class=\" \">Replace With &gt; Previous from Local History</strong>, and Studio will automatically revert the file to the previously saved version.)    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>On the top part of the <strong class=\" \">Compare</strong> window, select the date/time that corresponds to the version with which you want to replace the current version. You can preview the changes by double clicking the date/time, and Studio will display the changes in the bottom part of the window.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Click the <strong class=\" \">Replace</strong> button to replace the current file with the selected version.    </p>\n</li></ol>        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=30083314\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Rolling Back a File Version"});